    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="集群故障排查日志-slurm-nodestate-down">集群故障排查日志-slurmnodestate down</h1><ul><li><p>今天是不知道为什么slurm节点状态变成了down，尝试了几次，在、要注意的点首先是修改slurm登录的账户要是和以前配置slurm的一样。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sinfo <span class="hljs-comment">#发现node 状态是down</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#切换到root</span><br>sudo scontrol update NodeName=node08 State=idle<br>或者<br>sudo scontrol update NodeName=node08 State=RESUME<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>搞定收工</p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
