  <entry>
    <title>Vasp进程自动被杀掉</title>
    <link href="/year/04/27/%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97-vasp%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8Evasp%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD/"/>
    <url>/year/04/27/%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97-vasp%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8Evasp%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="如题">如题</h1><p>这个我先排查了内存情况，查看了系统日志，</p><p>dmesg | egrep -i -B100 'killed process'</p><p>发现是linux杀死了这个 因为内存占用过大。</p><p>修改参数NCORE 调小内存占用</p>]]></content>
    
    
